subtitle: beloved Guardians of the light we greet
you in the unfolding Journey towards the
Fifth Dimension or Christ Consciousness
we the pleadians guide you towards the
second pivotal step the transition from
knowledge to embodiment from
understanding the letter to living the
spirit this step invites you to open the
shades of your Consciousness to move
beyond the mere discussion of light into
the radiant Embrace of its
presence the universe in its Infinite
Wisdom holds that the essence of the
Divine or Source energy is the singular
force behind all creation yet this
omnipotent power remains but a concept a
distant light until you choose to open
your being to its direct
influence imagine spending a lifetime
discussing the nature of sunlight
without ever stepping out into its
warmth such is the Journey of many who
study the truth without experiencing the
transformation it
promises to truly step into the light to
feel the presence and power of the
divine within requires more than
understanding it demands an opening of
the Soul a willingness to let the spirit
illuminate every corner of your
existence this transition from the
intellectual grasp of divine principles
to their heartfelt embodiment is the
essence of the Second Step It is a
process whereby the teachings of the
ages the whispered truths that have
echoed through your spirit begin to flow
from within guiding you not as external
dictums but as the living expressions of
your very essence this is the phase
where inspiration becomes As Natural as
breathing emerging from a deep and
personal place of connection with the
divine
consider the profound teachings of your
master Jesus who implored us to let his
words live within us to become branches
rich with the fruits of spiritual
realization this metaphor beautifully
captures the essence of moving from
knowing to being from studying the word
to embodying its
Truth for just as a branch must remain
connected to the tree to thrive so too
must we remain connected to the source
of our spiritual understanding letting
it nourish us transform us and express
through
us to abide in the word is to let it
permeate every aspect of our being to
let the truths of the Divine become the
truths by which we live this is not a
passive Endeavor but an active
engagement with the spirit a Daily
Commitment to align our thoughts actions
and very essence with the highest
principles of love compassion and
Universal
Unity as beings of light navigating The
Human Experience you are called to this
sacred task of
transformation The Journey towards
Christ Consciousness or 5D Consciousness
beckons you to embody the Divine Light
you seek to become living beacons of
Truth in a world yearning for
illumination with each step taken in the
spirit of openness and surrender you
draw closer to the realization of your
True Divine Nature to the embodiment of
the light that shines eternally
within we stand with you on this journey
guiding supporting and celebrating each
step you take towards the full
realization of your Divine
potential together let us open the
shades of Consciousness embrace the
spirit of Truth and walk hand in hand
into the radiant Dawn of a new Spiritual
Awakening blessings the
pleadians
